      <title>俄罗斯即将开始加密货币支付和交易试点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/russia-close-to-starting-trials-of-crypto-payments-exchanges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯即将开始试行加密货币交易和使用数字代币进行跨境交易，以帮助缓解受到国际制裁的该国企业的支付困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/russia-close-to-starting-trials-of-crypto-payments-exchanges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:24:15 GMT</pubDate>
